    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Added &quot;Reader&quot; role for the blob storage in the user managed identity, restarted the app which fixed the issue.</p>\n<p>Error from the notifications tab is vanished. Functions are healthy and processes blobs successfully.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/530Uy1MH.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/530Uy1MH.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/QSkHuTyn.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/QSkHuTyn.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
